Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,=======TEXT=======
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.59,0:01:41.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛特·科内利下士
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.20,0:01:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.08,0:01:44.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,编入第三小队
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.72,0:01:45.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.90,0:01:47.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃玛·怀兹中士
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.28,0:01:47.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.23,0:01:49.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同为第三小队
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.78,0:01:50.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.85,0:01:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊安·布鲁诺上等兵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.50,0:01:53.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.37,0:01:54.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,编入第六小队
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.07,0:01:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.17,0:01:58.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维尔金·巩特尔少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.17,0:01:58.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.33,0:02:00.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巩特尔？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.05,0:02:01.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非是那个巩特尔…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.75,0:02:04.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任命你为第七小队队长
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.33,0:02:08.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么 有问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.11,0:02:09.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.48,0:02:11.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是名至实归
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.41,0:02:14.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高中接受过机械化部队训练
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.47,0:02:18.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也已通过大学的后备军官教程
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.59,0:02:24.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,况且你还是加利亚的英雄 巩特尔将军的儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.81,0:02:26.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 帕罗特上尉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.81,0:02:31.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有实战经验 突然被任命为小队长…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.33,0:02:33.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说你在布鲁鲁撤退战斗中表现活跃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.96,0:02:38.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们认为你已有实战经验
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.89,0:02:41.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话 我有一个请求
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.76,0:02:43.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么 说来听听
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.76,0:02:48.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能否允许使用布鲁鲁撤退时获得的战斗车辆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.58,0:02:49.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗车辆？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.24,0:02:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那辆战车与众不同
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.36,0:02:55.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有极少数人能够进行日常保养
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.34,0:02:56.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.62,0:03:01.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这么一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.60,0:03:08.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 将伊莎拉·巩特尔下士编入第七小队
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.53,0:03:09.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.53,0:03:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巩特尔少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.16,0:03:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你今后可能出于各种原因备受关注
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.22,0:03:18.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期待你的战果
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.05,0:03:19.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.41,0:03:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾丽西娅·梅尔姬沃特中士
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.33,0:03:22.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.24,0:03:26.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在第七小队 作为巩特尔少尉的下级士官
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.43,0:03:27.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,协助他工作
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.10,0:03:29.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.38,0:03:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保持严肃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.79,0:03:31.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,复述呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.95,0:03:34.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 辅佐巩特尔少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.15,0:03:36.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苏茜·埃文斯上等兵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.97,0:03:37.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.77,0:03:40.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我偏偏是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.50,0:03:44.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维尔金身边的下级士官啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.54,0:03:48.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么  为什么是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.42,0:03:50.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.62,0:03:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还能怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.19,0:03:56.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不可能明白我的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.39,0:04:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兴冲冲报名参加义勇军
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.21,0:04:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却遇上这种怪人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.32,0:04:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维尔金·巩特尔少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.09,0:04:11.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 久违了 维尔金
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.25,0:04:14.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法尔迪奥 这不是法尔迪奥吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.19,0:04:21.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.24,0:04:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢…谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.52,0:04:27.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来法尔迪奥也参加了义勇军
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.13,0:04:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我是第一小队的队长
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.75,0:04:34.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没去正规军啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.88,0:04:35.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.34,0:04:40.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问 两位是什么关系？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.77,0:04:42.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大学同学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.58,0:04:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维尔金是生物学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.40,0:04:46.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是考古学专业
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.55,0:04:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,专业不同 却好像很熟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.36,0:04:54.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.82,0:04:59.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非要解释的话 可能是“臭味相投”吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.92,0:05:02.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 说不定真的是喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.93,0:05:06.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说 他也是个怪人？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.22,0:05:10.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到啊 维尔金
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.43,0:05:14.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟然如此快就决定参加义勇军
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.81,0:05:17.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对战争那么反感的你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.62,0:05:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.48,0:05:23.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…全民皆兵制度下 没人能够例外
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.20,0:05:25.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.65,0:05:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃避兵役 办法有的是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.53,0:05:30.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想去国外避难的话 理应也不难
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.37,0:05:37.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布鲁鲁被占领时 我也在当地
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.72,0:05:41.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼见人们在战争中死去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.77,0:05:46.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现场目睹残垣断壁的城市与被毁的风车 我想
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.87,0:05:52.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须尽早结束这场战争
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.07,0:05:55.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了大家能重返家园
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.96,0:05:57.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有战斗的义务
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.85,0:05:59.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维尔金
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.66,0:06:01.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.86,0:06:05.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎到义勇军来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.91,0:06:09.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后我们就是战友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.62,0:06:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.54,0:06:17.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全队立正
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.69,0:06:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面由第七小队队长发表上任讲话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.11,0:06:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 维尔…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.39,0:06:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巩特尔少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.68,0:06:29.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 不用勉强
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.76,0:06:35.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是维尔金·巩特尔 今天开始与你们并肩作战
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.42,0:06:36.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.88,0:06:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家别这么拘谨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.15,0:06:46.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍…稍息
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.13,0:06:54.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 大学里的菜鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.81,0:06:56.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连实战经验都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.97,0:06:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一本正经当起队长来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.51,0:07:02.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 很是不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.54,0:07:08.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉鲁高·波特中士
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.16,0:07:10.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布丽奇特·修塔克下士
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.45,0:07:12.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明显不服维尔金呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.61,0:07:14.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心情倒也能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.14,0:07:18.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先 有件事想问大家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.49,0:07:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗中最重要的是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.55,0:07:24.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.90,0:07:26.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种还用问
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.48,0:07:28.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经验啊 经验
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.55,0:07:31.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 经验确实重要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.86,0:07:34.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不是最重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.33,0:07:38.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最重要的是你们的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.56,0:07:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么天真烂漫的蠢话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.83,0:07:48.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随着战斗进行 会遇到各种情况
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.65,0:07:50.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛苦与欢乐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.75,0:07:52.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愉快与悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.03,0:07:56.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些都只有活着才能品尝到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.01,0:07:58.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死了意味着一切的终结
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.90,0:08:01.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论陷入何种情况
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.34,0:08:04.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要活着就有希望
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.05,0:08:06.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点希望大家铭记在心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.63,0:08:08.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珍惜生命
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.93,0:08:11.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后我带领这支小队
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.22,0:08:15.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发誓会尽全力保护你们的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.55,0:08:20.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以希望你们也尽全力活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.82,0:08:21.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说完了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.31,0:08:32.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“不论陷入何种情况”
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.41,0:08:35.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“只要活着就有希望”
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.41,0:08:37.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是比唱得还好听
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.86,0:08:41.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大学高材生果然不同凡响
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.81,0:08:42.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点没错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.01,0:08:46.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想靠那么泛泛的演讲让我们乖乖听话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.09,0:08:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真够衰运的 偏偏遇上那样的队长
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.48,0:08:58.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此之前 这支小队另有一个不容忽视的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.61,0:09:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个围披肩的女孩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.74,0:09:10.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.05,0:09:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对是达鲁库斯人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.99,0:09:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我军防线在帝国军的攻势下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.94,0:09:20.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被迫退至本土内地 这就是现状
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.31,0:09:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我们不会永远被动挨打
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.79,0:09:29.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现正规军与义勇军正在进行部队重编
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.36,0:09:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待重整旗鼓后 立即伺机反击
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.84,0:09:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我军的第一个目标就是这里 沃塞尔市
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.08,0:09:38.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沃塞尔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.90,0:09:42.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,众所周知 沃塞尔市系交通枢纽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.83,0:09:44.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加之沃塞尔桥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.40,0:09:49.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是首都兰蒂格瑞丝沿岸道路途中最关键所在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.70,0:09:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即是说 敌人的利剑直刺我们咽喉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.85,0:09:55.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.31,0:09:58.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这座桥梁最终落入谁手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.27,0:10:00.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将在很大程度上左右今后战局
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.86,0:10:03.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我义勇军完成再编制后
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.85,0:10:06.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迅速出击前往沃塞尔市
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.35,0:10:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各小队加紧做好出击准备 完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.20,0:10:10.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.49,0:10:31.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾丽西娅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.67,0:10:32.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.22,0:10:35.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在开始就神经紧绷的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.43,0:10:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真到危急时不会泄气吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.39,0:10:42.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我就得像队长大人这样乐哈哈的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.84,0:10:44.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好严肃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.67,0:10:47.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 确实是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.39,0:10:49.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说…你这人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.11,0:10:53.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你瞧 正规军先一步出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.32,0:10:57.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定沃塞尔已经被一举拿下咯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.78,0:10:59.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看 是沃塞尔市
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.97,0:11:15.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来形势发展并不顺利啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.96,0:11:21.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚来没多久 战斗就陷入胶着状态吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.92,0:11:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说正规军强行渡桥 被打得落花流水
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.72,0:11:30.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难为他们了 其他桥梁全部被敌人攻陷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.63,0:11:33.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是唯一的渡河途径
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.17,0:11:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话 这场战斗可能会旷日持久
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.45,0:11:42.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 贸然动手只会增加牺牲者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.21,0:11:44.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受不了你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.89,0:11:46.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上从我们眼前消失！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.14,0:11:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.69,0:11:52.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么 非要我明说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.53,0:11:54.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 这是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.45,0:11:57.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好 队长大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.54,0:11:59.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们打开窗户说亮话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.25,0:12:01.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.88,0:12:03.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还看不出来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.55,0:12:06.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们无法容忍和达鲁库斯人并肩作战
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.61,0:12:07.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.51,0:12:08.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有同感
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.75,0:12:13.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自古以来人们都说达鲁库斯人是灾星
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.11,0:12:14.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.64,0:12:15.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.44,0:12:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有实战经验的毛头小子再指手画脚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.32,0:12:21.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不会有人听你的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.91,0:12:26.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太碍眼了 整天披着达鲁库斯花纹的衣裳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.66,0:12:29.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我确实是达鲁库斯人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.37,0:12:33.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我也和你们一样是人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.66,0:12:38.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 「达鲁库斯之灾」是没有科学依据的传说而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.49,0:12:41.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 按你这么说我是在无理取闹了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.38,0:12:44.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 不如打个赌怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.35,0:12:46.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.03,0:12:49.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们不愿服从我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.50,0:12:51.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想令你们服从
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.12,0:12:54.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么打赌就是最省事的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.91,0:12:55.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.01,0:12:58.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种场合下 难道让我们扔硬币？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.66,0:13:03.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来最大的问题是 我是否有作为队长的资格
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.41,0:13:07.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就等2天 2天内见分晓
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.89,0:13:09.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维尔金？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.62,0:13:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向你们保证 48小时内
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.72,0:13:17.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只靠这支第七小队 夺回那座桥梁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.19,0:13:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你他妈疯了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.27,0:13:22.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果没有成功
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.28,0:13:24.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自动辞职
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.53,0:13:27.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功的话 大家要服从我的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.60,0:13:28.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.83,0:13:31.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话既已出口 不得反悔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.81,0:13:33.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.37,0:13:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 交涉成立
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.37,0:13:41.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底在想什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.92,0:13:44.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.85,0:13:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是燕子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.20,0:13:53.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正规军都没完成的任务 单凭我们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.05,0:13:56.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还要在两天以内夺回那座桥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.93,0:13:58.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想想也不可能嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.50,0:14:03.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 难道是在为我担心？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.42,0:14:05.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么可能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.33,0:14:08.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船到桥前自然直
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.41,0:14:12.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么才能像你那样晴空万里啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.73,0:14:13.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到天气
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.58,0:14:17.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天早上天气应该不错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.64,0:14:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我们来说…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.85,0:14:23.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是2天 可能会更快
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.01,0:14:24.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.06,0:14:27.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾丽西娅 通知大家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.68,0:14:30.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明晨05:00 作战开始
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.31,0:14:33.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 完全看不透
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.78,0:14:35.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙到底在想什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.12,0:14:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维尔金…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.19,0:14:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.83,0:14:45.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事 就叫维尔金
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.98,0:14:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 维尔金
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.24,0:14:49.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道会起雾？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.80,0:14:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雾是空气中的水蒸气遇冷引起的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.63,0:15:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 还有燕子飞过
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.86,0:15:01.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燕子？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.71,0:15:07.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燕子低飞是高空空气变冷的征兆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.28,0:15:10.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么说 昨天的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.80,0:15:12.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.69,0:15:16.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 接下来得忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.93,0:15:23.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们第七小队对东岸敌人防卫据点发动奇袭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.25,0:15:24.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.64,0:15:28.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算有雾气掩护 靠这点人数渡桥…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.09,0:15:29.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不渡桥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.73,0:15:32.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡的是 这条河
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.85,0:15:35.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不靠坦克掩护？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.93,0:15:37.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等同于命令我们去送死…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.56,0:15:40.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心好啦 有坦克
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.28,0:15:42.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈 你的坦克能上天？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.91,0:15:43.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,类似吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.18,0:15:46.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但并非上天 而是下水
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.16,0:15:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.49,0:15:51.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们驾驶这辆Edelweiss号渡河
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.14,0:15:53.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在搞笑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.85,0:15:58.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坦克这东西不是在水里游 是在地上跑的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.34,0:16:00.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定脑子不正常
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.64,0:16:03.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从没听说过乘坦克过河的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.93,0:16:08.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 所以才有它的价值
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.12,0:16:12.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传达作战内容
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.42,0:16:17.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Edelweiss号立即准备渡河
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.27,0:16:20.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,步兵部队船上待命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.71,0:16:23.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认己方炮火后开始靠岸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.48,0:16:25.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一鼓作气拿下敌方据点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.23,0:16:29.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位 我们第七小队的第一份工作来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.18,0:16:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打起精神吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.20,0:16:36.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙 真打算去？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.42,0:16:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.70,0:16:44.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 都因为我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.39,0:16:46.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事 反倒帮大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.12,0:16:51.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,团结这支小队 这是必经之路
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.59,0:16:54.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 没有伊莎拉的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.69,0:16:56.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作战行动也无法成立
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.10,0:17:01.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,防水处理能坚持多久 必须在实战中才能验证
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.13,0:17:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 让你陪我冒险
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.88,0:17:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我相信哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.61,0:17:11.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包括Edelweiss号
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.94,0:17:14.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.59,0:17:16.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.71,0:17:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 作战开始
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.80,0:17:27.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也开始行动
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.56,0:17:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距离对岸还有300米
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.13,0:17:41.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理论极限潜水时间剩余2分40秒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.39,0:17:43.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠你了 Edelweiss
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.60,0:17:45.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距离对岸250米
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.10,0:18:00.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维尔金
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.74,0:18:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩余200
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.93,0:18:09.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提高功率 引擎熄火等同于作战失败
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.89,0:18:10.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.04,0:18:29.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么情况
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.82,0:18:32.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3分钟已经过了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.48,0:18:38.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.42,0:18:43.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.85,0:18:59.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡河完成
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.97,0:19:00.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分离
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.79,0:19:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 攻击开始
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.02,0:19:18.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙 真给他去到对岸了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.21,0:19:20.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始移动
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.33,0:19:21.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保持速度
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.02,0:19:24.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能让敌人摸清我们的兵力数量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.84,0:19:25.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.45,0:19:35.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌…敌袭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.87,0:19:36.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,数量是？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.84,0:19:37.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不明
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.27,0:19:39.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能 哪里冒出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.64,0:19:58.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右转20 发射
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.20,0:20:11.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北面 集中增援北面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.93,0:20:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被完全包围了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.54,0:20:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大势已去…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.25,0:20:53.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.66,0:20:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺利得让人吃惊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.04,0:21:01.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没你这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.36,0:21:05.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照约定 你们今后必须服从队长指示
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.86,0:21:06.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.24,0:21:10.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听队长的倒也无妨
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.66,0:21:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我绝不接纳达鲁库斯人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.16,0:21:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说…这算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.71,0:21:23.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.43,0:21:25.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾丽西娅 算了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.19,0:21:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,习以为常了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.86,0:21:27.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊莎拉…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,=======ED=======
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.46,0:21:46.83,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}君に会いたくて　夜明けも待たずに
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.21,0:21:50.84,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}走り出していた
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.13,0:21:56.78,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}思い出は僕を　海辺に導く
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.07,0:22:01.67,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}今もう一度飛んでみるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.97,0:22:05.95,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}あの風にのって
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.80,0:22:16.37,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}心地良さばかりを　求めて生きていた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.62,0:22:20.44,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}ぐるぐる同じ場所で
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.51,0:22:26.18,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}そんな僕の前に　現れた笑顔は
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.47,0:22:29.91,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}太陽のようだった
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.87,0:22:38.37,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}君に会いたくて　夜明けも待たずに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.67,0:22:42.48,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}走り出していた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.61,0:22:48.14,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}笑い合えるように　唄い合えるように
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.45,0:22:53.25,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}今もう一度飛んでみるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.44,0:22:57.13,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}あの風にのって
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.46,0:21:46.83,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}太想见你 不等天明
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.21,0:21:50.84,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}就飞奔出门
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.13,0:21:56.78,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}回忆将我 引向海边
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.07,0:22:01.67,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}此刻真想再次飞翔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.97,0:22:05.95,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}乘风飞翔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.80,0:22:16.37,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}一味追求安逸的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.62,0:22:20.44,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}原地踏步不前
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.51,0:22:26.18,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}出现在我面前的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.47,0:22:29.91,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}像太阳般灿烂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.87,0:22:38.37,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}太想见你 不等天明
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.67,0:22:42.48,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}就飞奔出门
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.61,0:22:48.14,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}想和你共同欢笑歌唱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.45,0:22:53.25,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}此刻真想再次飞翔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.44,0:22:57.13,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}乘风飞翔
